{"tid":2282645,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際社會譴責 英外相轟侵害港自治","createTime":"2020-11-12T03:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T04:45:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7aa7883a41c24379b1a028e8019a3570d669fa0","tid":2282645,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:56:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/66VWHOKZEBH3VN43FIMTJKWX3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2F66VWHOKZEBH3VN43FIMTJKWX3U%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2AuxBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=65cba781\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2F66VWHOKZEBH3VN43FIMTJKWX3U%2F&h=cba0779d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/66VWHOKZEBH3VN43FIMTJKWX3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國際社會譴責 英外相轟侵害港自治<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全國人大常。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：初選獲勝 抗爭派未定會否戰立會<br />\n<br />\n由18個國家和歐洲議會逾百名議員組成的「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」發表聲明，對DQ四名民主派議員作出最強烈譴責，指此舉對香港高度自治是「不可接受的攻擊」，並指「這種公然違反國際法的舉動，由非民選的全國人大常委會作出，反映中共和習近平班子蔑視港人和他們的民主價值」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指獨立的反對派，是維持人權、法治、政治自由和民主進程的關鍵，這些東西也是香港基本自由和獨特生活模式的重要部份。強推港版國安法和此舉，反映中國政府「決心強行終結一國兩制原則」。聯盟呼籲成員所屬國政府向中國領導層及其在港代理人採取緊急行動，就侵犯港人和違反國際法問責。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：區議員料中共不罷休 有被DQ準備<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PzI8NBL9nszU12TPy6Y_Zp_EYrc=/5472x3648/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C2JFU7FQHJCP7EFOGYLRR2KYTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPzI8NBL9nszU12TPy6Y_Zp_EYrc%3D%2F5472x3648%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC2JFU7FQHJCP7EFOGYLRR2KYTQ.jpg&h=e4a2695c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國外相藍韜文 路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彭定康：中共踐踏民主制度<br />\n<br />\n末代港督彭定康批評這是中共踐踏香港民主制度的又一個例子，「習近平政權再次表明它完全敵視民主問責及為此站出來的人士」。英國前外相聶偉敬（Malcolm Rifkind）形容習近平終結一國兩制，「我們向民主派人士以總辭抗議致敬，他們是巨人，中國政府顯得渺小」。<br />\n<br />\n英國上議員奧爾頓勳爵（David Alton）指中共雖暫時令民選議員消音，卻終會擋不住民主運動的洪流，「冒起的世代將向拒絕屈服的議員的勇氣致敬」。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）指，人大常委決議「實質上關閉了香港市民一條表達政治異議剩下不多的渠道」。"},{"pid":"686ac1b9fe0a0ae2a2214c3cd69876cb03768d95","tid":2282645,"uid":255976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"講有L用咩，制裁淋病一眾官員啦"},{"pid":"3b3395e26341ed002593704bd2d50947ac27bea9","tid":2282645,"uid":316354,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"開頭睇錯 以為trump做錯左啲咩"},{"pid":"41942f45f0c3d677e398963d3f9016acabf98a1b","tid":2282645,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3b3395e26341ed002593704bd2d50947ac27bea9","tid":2282645,"uid":316354,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"開頭睇錯 以為trump做錯左啲咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"Me2<br />\n開始明點解唔直接叫Trump做侵"},{"pid":"c41634b41652d8ba0541b5b7955e26974d6a5373","tid":2282645,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41942f45f0c3d677e398963d3f9016acabf98a1b","tid":2282645,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3b3395e26341ed002593704bd2d50947ac27bea9","tid":2282645,"uid":316354,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"開頭睇錯 以為trump做錯左啲咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"Me2<br />\n開始明點解唔直接叫Trump做侵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:39:18.000Z","msg":"me3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫trump好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d054b83053ed9c0f017a2c34824000583e8172","tid":2282645,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"